  "excerpt": "<p style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>帝雉石進駐鳴日廚房，打造台鐵美學觀光新體驗！</strong></p>",
  "thumbnail": "/images/1752483346819-X19EZZDZWEXBNMXDGGW0/_.jpg",
  "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"sqs-layout sqs-grid-12 columns-12\" data-layout-label=\"Post Body\" data-type=\"item\" id=\"item-6874c6126a2003590e8bd09f\"><div class=\"row sqs-row\"><div class=\"col sqs-col-12 span-12\"><div class=\"sqs-block website-component-block sqs-block-website-component sqs-block-html html-block\" data-block-css=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.html/d92a980d-b660-49d1-a8a9-d817239fa29e_741/website.components.html.styles.css&quot;]\" data-block-scripts=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.html/d92a980d-b660-49d1-a8a9-d817239fa29e_741/website.components.html.visitor.js&quot;]\" data-block-type=\"1337\" data-definition-name=\"website.components.html\" data-sqsp-block=\"text\" data-website-component-id=\"52d79453219c41da8731\" id=\"block-52d79453219c41da8731\"><div class=\"sqs-block-content\"><div class=\"sqs-text-block-container\">\n  \n  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><h3 style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>帝雉石與台鐵美學觀光列車「鳴日廚房」絕配秘密！<br></strong>與五星餐車齊名，<strong>譜寫融合藝術性與實用性的動人樂章</strong></h3></div>\n\n\n  \n<style id=\"container-styles\">#block-52d79453219c41da8731 {\n    \n    --stroke-style: none;--stroke-thickness: 6px;\n    \n      \n      \n      \n    \n\n--tweak-text-block-background-color: initial;\n\n  }\n\n  #block-52d79453219c41da8731 .sqs-html-content {\n    \n    --tweak-text-block-padding: 6% 6% 6% 6%;\n  --tweak-text-block-padding: initial;\n}\n\n  #block-52d79453219c41da8731 {\n      mix-blend-mode: var(--tweak-text-block-blend\n  );\n      border-radius: var(--tweak-text-block-radius);\n  }\n\n  \n  \n#block-52d79453219c41da8731 {\n      --tweak-text-block-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\n    }\n\n\n  \n  \n\n  #block-52d79453219c41da8731 {\n    }\n\n</style>\n\n<style id=\"override-container-styles\">\n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          